snippet.title: Desiya Thalaivar Official Trailer | Aravind Raj | J M Bashir | Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja | SSR SATHYA
snippet.description:
Get a glimpse into the life and times of the revered national leader Pasumpon Muthuramalinga Thevar in the upcoming Tamil biographical film, Desiya Thalaivar (The National Leader).

Directed by R. Aravind Raj (known for films like Oomai Vizhigal and Uzhavan Magan), this much-anticipated biopic explores Thevar's contributions as a freedom fighter, his involvement in social movements like the Temple Entry movement, and his political journey.

The film stars J.M. Bashir in the titular role, portraying the celebrated leader. The music for the film is scored by the legendary Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja.

Desiya Thalaivar promises to be a powerful and inspiring cinematic tribute to one of Tamil Nadu's most influential historical figures.

Cast & Crew:

Starring: J.M. Bashir, Bharathiraja, Radharavi (and others)

Director: R. Aravind Raj

Music: Ilaiyaraaja

Producers: SS.Satya, S. Jennifer Margaret 

Production: SSR SATHYA

Ikk Kudi promises to be more than just a film‚Äîit‚Äôs a statement. With strong storytelling and a subject that resonates with today‚Äôs generation, the film is already building buzz across social media. Whether you're a fan of Punjabi cinema or drawn to stories of strength and individuality, Ikk Kudi looks set to leave a mark.

Lyrics: 
O‚Ä¶Madhana manamohini nee yarale
Kande manamohaka maayaakale
Bhaavaneya baraseledha shoora shaakunthale
Meluvaage aralidhe manadhi prema kaavyangale‚Ä¶
Are eno badhalaadha haagidhe
Malebillondhu maigantidhe
Samara salugeyaadhanthe

Charithe naduve mudhdhaadha
Kavithe Putava theredhu banthe

Sukhadha nadhiya suliyindha
Sakhiya hrudhya muligidhanthe‚Ä¶

Dil me hai tu mere qismat mein nahin 

Mar ke bhi toh zinda mujhme reh jaayega tu haan 

Na ho ke bhi pass mere tu mera hua 
Tujhse hi toh Saans chale tu mera hua

#HarshvardhanRane #SonamBajwa #DeewaniyatKiDiwali #Diwali2025.

snippet.title: Qubool (Song) | Haq | Vishal Mishra | Armaan Khan | Yami Gautam & Emraan Hashmi | In Cinemas 7 Nov
snippet.description:
One word, countless emotions ‚Äì Qubool is here to touch your soul. The much-awaited track is finally out, and it‚Äôs nothing short of magical. With heartfelt lyrics, soulful vocals, and a melody that lingers long after it ends, Qubool captures the raw essence of love, longing, and acceptance. Every beat carries depth, and every word resonates with the kind of emotion that stays with you.

Whether you're in love, healing, or simply a fan of meaningful music, 'Qubool' is a song that speaks to the heart. It's the kind of track you‚Äôll want to put on repeat.

#Qubool #HAqSongs #LoveSong #RomanticSong #NewSong #TrendingSong #YamiGautam #EmraanHashmi #VishalMishra #ArmaanKhan #QuboolHai

Directed by- Suparn S Varma
Produced by- Vineet Jain
Produced by- Vishal Gurnani, Juhi Parekh Mehta, Harman Baweja
Co-Produced by- Amrita Pandey, Suparn S Varma, Rowena Baweja, Sandeep Singh
Written by- Reshu Nath | Music by - Vishal Mishra
Releasing in cinemas on 7th November

Song Credits 
Composer : Vishal Mishra
Lyrics : Kaushal Kishore
Singer : Armaan Khan 
Arrangement & Production : Vishal Mishra
Music Production by : Gaurav Vaswani
Additional Production : Kandarpa Kalita, Bitupon Boruah
Additional Vocals - Vishal Mishra 
Music Assistant : Kumar Gaurav Singh ,Trihangku Lahkar,Bitupon Boruah
Mixed & Mastered by : Trihangku Lahkar @VMS

Strokes : Tapas Roy
Acoustic Guitar : Kandarpa Kalita
Live Rhythm Arranged by : Prashant Sonagra & Swaranjay Dhumal
Tabla : Prashant Sonagra
Dholak : Mushtak Khan & Ishteyak Khan
Percussions : Swaranjay Dhumal, Prashant Sonagra, Harsh Bhoir & Mohit Kathak

Live Rhythms, Strokes Recorded at YRF Studio by : Vijay Dayal, Sagar Sathe
Guitars, Vocals Recorded at VMS by : Trihangku Lahkar &¬†Bitupon¬†Boruah
YouTube Promotions: Navi Baadliwal

Lyrics:
Mila asman se koi noor kohinoor dastoor mera
Lo aaj se hua main, sadiyon ko tera‚Ä¶
Dekho zara dekho, naam tera likha hai
Mera hai jo mera, sab tera ho chuka hai
Dil pe ab na zor koi
Har qadam teri or hai
Saans hai khushboo bhari
Har raasta ab phool hai
Koi shart ho ya dard ho
Yeh raabta qubool hai
Saans hai khushboo bhari
Har raasta qubool hai
Qubool teri zid hai saari
Saari baatein qubool hain
Qubool saare din tumhaare
Siyah raatein qubool hain
Tu saaye-baan tu, teri chaanv mein khud ko bhulakar jhoom loon
Yoon tera hoon, tu dard de to dard ko bhi choom loon
Muskuraana hai tujh hi se, tujh se hi aaraam hai
Tu nahi to main nahi hoon, zindagi tere naam hai
Tu na to main bemaaine
Hona mera hi fizool hai
Koi shart ho ya dard ho
Yeh raabta qubool hai
Hai ishq mein jo doobe hum
Gham bhi mile to kaisa gham
Tera sahi tera galat
Tera jhooth bhi to qubool hai
Accha bura kya tolna
Kya mashwara kya sochna
Mahboob hota hai Khuda
Yahi ishq ka usool ha

In this video, me and my friend face the SCARIEST TAX MAN ever seen in Minecraft! snippet.title: Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!
snippet.description:
Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!


Instagram pe 50k kar do: https://www.instagram.com/psd_1/

In this video, I do a Minecraft deathswap challenge with my YouTuber friend @MrLapis 
where we both get 15 mins to build traps for each other, and as the timer finishes, our position gets swapped with each other. The player who survives in the end wins and gets Rs 50000!
